title: Yellow Note - 2003 - We Love Everybody...And You're Next!!! (FLA
description:
The first incarnations of Yellow Note were all on the drum'n'bass side of things, quite a departure from David Barratt's creation of commercials for Kraft, McDonalds, Hallmark, and his production of Barry Manilow and Celine Dion (not to mention his own jazz album). Fitting well on Jungle Sky, Yellow Note released a couple CDs and some vinyl, then disappeared for a few years.
